txt.en: Perfect Icy Rune-stone of the Galadhrim Scroll Case[E]
On opening, the scroll case will reveal the Perfect Icy Rune-stone of the Galadhrim recipe.\n\nYou must be friendly with the Galadhrim and Artisan of the Jeweller's Guild to use this item.
